text: Marta Blasco Sinfreu (born 19 June 2003) is an Andorran footballer who plays as a defender for the Andorra women's national team. ==International career== Blasco capped for Andorra at senior level in a 1–2 friendly loss to Luxembourg in June 2019. ==References== Category:2003 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football defenders Category:Andorran women's footballers Category:Andorra women's international footballers
